          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Promoting Apprenticeships in Public Service Act </b></p> <p>This bill establishes a student loan forgiveness program for borrowers who (1) receive a certificate from a registered apprenticeship program; and (2) complete two years of full-time, public-service employment. The amount forgiven is limited to $25,000. </p>]]></text>
